---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Chinook Driving School Calgary"
  description="Read the privacy policy for Chinook Driving School Calgary."
>
  <section class="bg-n-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto flex w-full max-w-4xl flex-col gap-6 px-6 py-16 lg:px-0 lg:py-24">
      <h1 class="text-n-800 text-3xl font-bold leading-tight lg:text-5xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-n-600 text-base leading-7">
        Chinook Driving School Calgary respects your privacy and is committed to protecting the
        personal information you share through our website, contact forms, and enrollment process.
      </p>
      <p class="text-n-600 text-base leading-7">
        We collect only the information needed to respond to inquiries, process enrollments,
        communicate scheduling details, and support your driver training experience.
      </p>
      <p class="text-n-600 text-base leading-7">
        If you have any questions about how your information is used, please contact our team
        directly through the contact page.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
